msgctxt "1392_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Oh, you're back!"
msgstr "¡Oh, has vuelto!"

msgctxt "1440_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Hello."
msgstr "Hola."

msgctxt "1452_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-san... You aren't requesting me today?"
msgstr "Oh, Kiryu-san... You aren't requesting me today?"

msgctxt "1464_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Oh, I got a request."
msgstr "Oh, me han solicitado."

msgctxt "1476_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Enjoy your stay, okay?"
msgstr "Disfruta de tu estancia, ¿sí?"

msgctxt "1488_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Bye then."
msgstr "Nos vemos."

msgctxt "1500_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Hi! It's nice to meet you!"
msgstr "Hi! It's nice to meet you!"

msgctxt "1512_Kiryu"
msgid "You're certainly full of energy."
msgstr "You're certainly full of energy."

msgctxt "1524_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "I'm just getting started! My shows only get more exciting as time goes on!"
msgstr "I'm just getting started! My shows only get more exciting as time goes on!"

msgctxt "1536_Kiryu"
msgid "Your shows?"
msgstr "Your shows?"

msgctxt "1548_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Oh, never mind about that. So, what's your name?"
msgstr "Oh, never mind about that. So, what's your name?"

msgctxt "1560_Kiryu"
msgid "Kazuma Kiryu."
msgstr "Kazuma Kiryu."

msgctxt "1572_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Hello, Kiryu-san. I like that name. Very cool. And you've got quite a body on you."
msgstr "Hello, Kiryu-san. I like that name. Very cool. And you've got quite a body on you."

msgctxt "1584_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Are you an athlete? Maybe a fighter? You look like a fighter."
msgstr "Are you an athlete? Maybe a fighter? You look like a fighter."

msgctxt "1596_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Actually, I think I've seen you somewhere before."
msgstr "Actually, I think I've seen you somewhere before."

msgctxt "1608_Kiryu"
msgid "You must be imagining that. Could be you're confusing me with somebody else."
msgstr "You must be imagining that. Could be you're confusing me with somebody else."

msgctxt "1620_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Really? But Kiryu-san, you do like to fight, right?"
msgstr "Really? But Kiryu-san, you do like to fight, right?"

msgctxt "1632_Kiryu"
msgid "If I have to."
msgstr "If I have to."

msgctxt "1644_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "I'd love to see you fight!"
msgstr "I'd love to see you fight!"

msgctxt "1656_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "I love martial arts. There's nothing I like more than a good street fight. Just watching, of course! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "I love martial arts. There's nothing I like more than a good street fight. Just watching, of course! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "1668_Kiryu"
msgid "I see..."
msgstr "Ya veo..."

msgctxt "1680_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Maybe you could call me next time you're going to fight. I'll come and watch."
msgstr "Maybe you could call me next time you're going to fight. I'll come and watch."

msgctxt "1692_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh, I'll see what I can do."
msgstr "Heh, I'll see what I can do."

msgctxt "1704_Kiryu"
msgid "Don't go spreading that around."
msgstr "Don't go spreading that around."

msgctxt "1716_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "I knew it! You're famous, aren't you!?"
msgstr "I knew it! You're famous, aren't you!?"

msgctxt "1728_Kiryu"
msgid "Hard to say. I haven't been to Kamurocho much recently."
msgstr "Hard to say. I haven't been to Kamurocho much recently."

msgctxt "1740_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Hm, I know I've seen you somewhere... Don't tell me, it'll come to me eventually."
msgstr "Hm, I know I've seen you somewhere... Don't tell me, it'll come to me eventually."

msgctxt "1752_Kiryu"
msgid "Maybe you have."
msgstr "Maybe you have."

msgctxt "1764_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Hehe. Well, let's talk while I think about it."
msgstr "Hehe. Well, let's talk while I think about it."

msgctxt "1776_Kiryu"
msgid "All right."
msgstr "Está bien."

msgctxt "1788_Kiryu"
msgid "You talk a lot, don't you?"
msgstr "You talk a lot, don't you?"

msgctxt "1800_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "You don't like women who talk a lot?"
msgstr "You don't like women who talk a lot?"

msgctxt "1812_Kiryu"
msgid "I didn't say that."
msgstr "I didn't say that."

msgctxt "1824_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Good, because that's one of the things people love about me."
msgstr "Good, because that's one of the things people love about me."

msgctxt "1836_Kiryu"
msgid "That's kind of a strange thing to say about yourself, isn't it?"
msgstr "That's kind of a strange thing to say about yourself, isn't it?"

msgctxt "1848_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Well, if nobody else will compliment me, I might as well do it myself, right?"
msgstr "Well, if nobody else will compliment me, I might as well do it myself, right?"

msgctxt "1860_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh, you're funny."
msgstr "Heh, you're funny."

msgctxt "1872_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Is that a compliment?"
msgstr "Is that a compliment?"

msgctxt "1884_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "You look kinda scary, but I bet you're a nice guy."
msgstr "You look kinda scary, but I bet you're a nice guy."

msgctxt "1896_Kiryu"
msgid "You think so?"
msgstr "¿De verdad lo cree?"

msgctxt "1908_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Yep. I'm sure of it! I have good instincts about these things."
msgstr "Yep. I'm sure of it! I have good instincts about these things."

msgctxt "1920_Kiryu"
msgid "Is that right?"
msgstr "Jo, ¿de verdad?"

msgctxt "1932_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "I bet I can tell what you're thinking right now."
msgstr "I bet I can tell what you're thinking right now."

msgctxt "1944_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh? That might be fun."
msgstr "Oh? That might be fun."

msgctxt "1956_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "I'm picking up a vibration... You wanna come again soon and request me!"
msgstr "I'm picking up a vibration... You wanna come again soon and request me!"

msgctxt "1968_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Was I right?"
msgstr "Was I right?"

msgctxt "1980_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh, what's up with that?"
msgstr "Heh, what's up with that?"

msgctxt "1992_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Bull's-eye, right? Pretty impressive, huh?"
msgstr "Bull's-eye, right? Pretty impressive, huh?"

msgctxt "2004_Kiryu"
msgid "Do you talk to spirits or something?"
msgstr "Do you talk to spirits or something?"

msgctxt "2016_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Sure. I've been seeing ghosts ever since I was little."
msgstr "Sure. I've been seeing ghosts ever since I was little."

msgctxt "2028_Kiryu"
msgid "Really? Wow..."
msgstr "Really? Wow..."

msgctxt "2040_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Just kidding! You didn't think I was being serious, did you?"
msgstr "Just kidding! You didn't think I was being serious, did you?"

msgctxt "2052_Kiryu"
msgid "Of course not. I was just playing along."
msgstr "Of course not. I was just playing along."

msgctxt "2064_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Haha! I think you and I are gonna get along just fine. I don't usually hit it off this well with folks when I first meet them."
msgstr "Haha! I think you and I are gonna get along just fine. I don't usually hit it off this well with folks when I first meet them."

msgctxt "2076_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "I hope you'll come again! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "I hope you'll come again! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2088_Kiryu"
msgid "I'll think about it."
msgstr "I'll think about it."

msgctxt "2100_Kiryu"
msgid "Sorry, but you got that one wrong."
msgstr "Sorry, but you got that one wrong."

msgctxt "2112_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Huh!? Really? You don't find me attractive?"
msgstr "Huh!? Really? You don't find me attractive?"

msgctxt "2124_Kiryu"
msgid "How can I tell? I hardly know you."
msgstr "How can I tell? I hardly know you."

msgctxt "2136_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Well, don't you want to talk to me so you can get to know me better?"
msgstr "Well, don't you want to talk to me so you can get to know me better?"

msgctxt "2148_Kiryu"
msgid "I suppose I could do that."
msgstr "I suppose I could do that."

msgctxt "2160_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "I knew it! See! I'm sure we'd have a good time if you came to see me again. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "I knew it! See! I'm sure we'd have a good time if you came to see me again. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2172_Kiryu"
msgid "You don't have to try so hard..."
msgstr "You don't have to try so hard..."

msgctxt "2184_Kiryu"
msgid "You might be right, actually."
msgstr "You might be right, actually."

msgctxt "2196_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Really!? So you'll come again?"
msgstr "Really!? So you'll come again?"

msgctxt "2208_Kiryu"
msgid "Sure."
msgstr "Claro."

msgctxt "2220_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Haha! I knew you'd come through! You totally caught my eye. I knew you were special as soon as I saw you! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Haha! I knew you'd come through! You totally caught my eye. I knew you were special as soon as I saw you! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2232_Kiryu"
msgid "You're laying it on a little thick, don't you think?"
msgstr "You're laying it on a little thick, don't you think?"

msgctxt "2244_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Hehe. You are gonna come again, right?"
msgstr "Hehe. You are gonna come again, right?"

msgctxt "2256_Kiryu"
msgid "Seems I don't have a choice..."
msgstr "Seems I don't have a choice..."

msgctxt "2268_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Hey! You came back! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Hey! You came back! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2280_Kiryu"
msgid "Well, I've been thinking about you."
msgstr "Well, I've been thinking about you."

msgctxt "2292_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Really? You shouldn't lie to an innocent girl like me, I might end up believing you! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Really? You shouldn't lie to an innocent girl like me, I might end up believing you! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2304_Kiryu"
msgid "I'm not lying. It's the truth."
msgstr "I'm not lying. It's the truth."

msgctxt "2316_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Oh, okay! Why don't you request me next time, then?"
msgstr "Oh, okay! Why don't you request me next time, then?"

msgctxt "2328_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh, I got the message..."
msgstr "Heh, I got the message..."

msgctxt "2340_Himeka"
msgid "The dialogue will end after one round if you've\\r\n"\n"entered a club more than once. Please report when this message is displayed."
msgstr "El diálogo terminará después de una ronda\\r\n"\n"cuando entre al club más de una vez. Contacte a un programador si ve este mensaje."

msgctxt "2352_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Kiryu-san..."
msgstr "Kiryu-san..."

msgctxt "2364_Kiryu"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "2376_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Why?"
msgstr "¿Tú?"

msgctxt "2388_Kiryu"
msgid "Why what?"
msgstr "Why what?"

msgctxt "2400_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Why didn't you request me?"
msgstr "Why didn't you request me?"

msgctxt "2412_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh, that. Sometimes I like to talk to other girls. There's nothing wrong with that, is there?"
msgstr "Oh, that. Sometimes I like to talk to other girls. There's nothing wrong with that, is there?"

msgctxt "2424_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "You could always request me and then invite another girl to join us?"
msgstr "You could always request me and then invite another girl to join us?"

msgctxt "2436_Kiryu"
msgid "Uh, I suppose so. Maybe I'll do that next time."
msgstr "Uh, I suppose so. Maybe I'll do that next time."

msgctxt "2448_望月京子：源氏名"
msgid "Really? I don't know if I can trust you..."
msgstr "Really? I don't know if I can trust you..."

msgctxt "2460_Himeka"
msgid "The dialogue will end after one round if you've\\r\n"\n"entered a club more than once. Please report when this message is displayed."
msgstr "El diálogo terminará después de una ronda\\r\n"\n"cuando entre al club más de una vez. Contacte a un programador si ve este mensaje."

